[36m(main_task pid=25904)[0m The cost of the calculator is \(1.20\).
[36m(main_task pid=25904)[0m The cost of the geometry set is \(10.00\).
[36m(main_task pid=25904)[0m The total cost of the items before the discount is \(7.50 + 0.50 + 1.20 + 10.00 = 19.20\).
